                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-180-off1108 t18210411-180-crimeloc1111"></join>. On the 27th of March, the prisoner was put in possession of the house, in execution for rent - he was there from nine o'clock until five in the afternoon, and after he left I missed two spoons, and found he had pawned one and redeemed it about an hour after. I sent for an officer, who took him, and he told where he sold it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210411-180-person1762">
                  WILLIAM 
                  COLTON
               <interp inst="t18210411-180-person1762" type="surname" value="COLTON"></interp>
